text: Raseuki nyang Kamoe bri keu gata Tameubeulanja zakeuet seudeukah F Yoh goh troh mawot keunan bak gata 5 Watee nyan gata meunyesai teulah Watee nyan takheun Tuhanku pakon Han Neupeutrep lon bek mate bagah Neubri bacut treuk keu lon nyoe watee Mangat jeuet teuntee lon bri seudeukah Amai nyang saleh lon pubuet teuma
